2) way to get master materia
1. magic master materia: master all magic materias and choose 1st choice
at the green materia
2. command master materia: master all command materias(steal, throw,
critical attack, change to item, control, analyze, and
copy) and choose 1st choice at the yellow materia
3. summom master masteria: master all summoom materia and choose 1st
choice at the red materia

3) proven facts
1. there are just 4 huge materias
2. caitsith has just 2 limit attacks
3. Aerith can be revived!!!!!

4) way to get W materias
1. W-item:go down when you are in the tunnel in the "stop the mad
science using the cannon!" event(last even on 2nd CD)
2. W-summon:get 640000 bps in gold sauser
3. W-magic:find it in the last dungeon

5) easy way go get status increasing potion
go to sunken ship and equip yufi with her best weapon and "change to an
item" materia. Then kill monsters with the change
command. All monsters in the sunken ship give the potions when they are
changed to items.
